1. *Ujutru* sam se probudio rano.(I woke up early in the morning)
2. *Ujutru* sam se pripremio za školu.(I prepared for school in the morning)
3. *Ujutru* je bilo tmurno i hladno.(It was cloudy and cold in the morning)
4. *Ujutru* je to bilo neočekivano.(It was unexpected in the morning)
5. *Ujutru* sam se spremao za posao.(I was getting ready for work in the morning)